{"tid":1828372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「釋放被捕人士」係指全部示威者，包括勇武！","createTime":"2020-01-17T18:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T06:04:02.000Z","uid":87553,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4845177fb5be8a351875619f53bd2375f2c7ec","tid":1828372,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"見到有人話和平示威可以放，傷人唔可以放，真係火撚滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢壇運動根本就係官逼民反，點解用武力就抵坐監？點解你哋可以享受勇武阻止送中通過，但係落手嘅手足就要受罰？<br />\n<br />\n重有，和平示威唔應該拉，小學生都知啦，又駛鬼特登搞成一個大訴求？由一開始，「釋放被捕人士」就係指所有對抗暴政嘅示威者，包括和平同勇武！<br />\n<br />\n當日612阻止送中招致嘅暴動罪要免除，之後所有以武制暴嘅義舉，全部都應該要免罪！如果唔係又講咩「釋放被捕人士」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">傳送門：梁家傑話輕罪先赦免，唔該連登仔入去教育下下佢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/12840197743/posts/10157807681397744/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F12840197743%2Fposts%2F10157807681397744%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=d4f55eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/12840197743/posts/10157807681397744/</a>"},{"pid":"ede9a35388526cf08a6a063ceec24c292ebd4f46","tid":1828372,"uid":137547,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:08:30.000Z","msg":"係指所有政治犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括2016年嘅梁天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ec6beb2f7e53714739bf7a89577c09e0556501","tid":1828372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"1. 嚴重傷人<br />\n示威者算係既一隻手數得哂<br />\n黑警有片既單單都係<br />\n<br />\n2. 哩種論點大把人講過<br />\n包括19，老燒<br />\n唔通19又係出賣<br />\n<br />\n多次衝突，警民仇怨利息大量疊加，即使成立獨立調查委員會，旗下可能也要就不同事件，分設小組，分別調查，工作量極為浩大，曠日持久。但至少可以讓社會各方都冷靜下來，讓時間沖淡創傷。<br />\n<br />\n然後由退休大法官領導的獨立調查委員會，可以就控罪問題，作出推薦（recommend）：少數證據確鑿的暴力者應予起訴，包括在騷亂中蓄意破壞公物、向建築物縱火、或在混亂中搶掠店舖（若有這類行為的話），但大多數警員和被捕人士，鑒於風暴是由「不撤回」的原點引起，建議不作刑事追究。<br />\n<br />\n這不是尊重法治與否的問題。而是事既至今，若起訴一千數百人暴動罪、刑事毁壞罪、襲警罪、縱火罪、公眾地方行為不檢；但一名警員也不交出來追究，在政治上，你以為風暴會平息？是否因此而又搞到引用基本法 18 條或緊急法例暴力讓升級？[/quote]"},{"pid":"690e818f09f43acf547a84b49fc2d94d5f486c17","tid":1828372,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53f4dAb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53f4dAb.gif&h=755d7b56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f41fad0d18fa53efdde21090b8809bf62c715e1e","tid":1828372,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T18:16:14.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"ce85dee4a370f6e589b05202a4339846b2e06655","tid":1828372,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:32:26.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc1b3ffd7ee86d9621d989cf992d5fe929c7bf","tid":1828372,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"所有人都要放"},{"pid":"7db08d6c5fb31218eeef5deb04c824ea33584727","tid":1828372,"uid":158889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"左膠由頭到尾都當勇武condom <br />\n<br />\n好心認清事實啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b460c53c923ca639e9fa97e34d8864fe470cb6","tid":1828372,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"梁家傑講的重罪不赦<br />\n<ins>實際攻擊立法會玻璃係重罪</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以享受完衝擊者反惡法的成果後走去出賣人</span>"},{"pid":"91601f31de4994cf91af1edcceb5205871ba2d2b","tid":1828372,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"飯民對示威者破壞公物就堅持追究<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想問呢班人有無幫過遭黑警輪姦的女仔出頭</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日講陶傑,老解單野都睇到條友幫中共放料,同現在唔係拜偶像"},{"pid":"b56aadf9bbda347922cffca33e33ef1008be2230","tid":1828372,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"左膠駁唔到仲叫人聽日出去被捕 不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a57c8a4c544349bef65a0048634d36920008f95","tid":1828372,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"記住啦 聽日做野你就係鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca67a8e9ca1dfa46df398d05bda15eb8f7576913","tid":1828372,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e27c3e641a701bb10308fbf3239ee44b6ec3b68a","tid":1828372,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f7dde259b368d6e9c4d770b7eb6dd003550670","tid":1828372,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b651ec9110f492db5d878f41440aa2d6af112b","tid":1828372,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"手足一個都不能少<br />\n邊個話勇武手足不赦嘅，光復後必遭清算"},{"pid":"d2ccba6b7e909f785f16a1c0f306cc637810906a","tid":1828372,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先易後難</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2864318296333bb9997e70585b453266a5c8d92","tid":1828372,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"勝者全取，我地輸就入集中營，贏就係建國英雄"},{"pid":"ee5962748633ec3f84e52710b9319b2ec69ed9ce","tid":1828372,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9662fcf37db468aab7a43bf1ea997c4586475872","tid":1828372,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2b086e0843058cb418f46b06e38051cd940d87","tid":1828372,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"總之，唔放人就保證鬥足三代，絕不妥協。<br />\n<br />\n果啲咩有冇得傾，態度變唔變軟果啲，一概唔撚知，放咗人再講。<br />\n<br />\n議員同政客影響到部分人，但係政府怕嘅絕對唔係呢部分，政權顧忌嘅係果班永不屈服嘅人，會縮嘅人洗撚驚，係咪先。<br />\n<br />\n真係要鬥企得硬，邊個縮先就會輸晒所有野，人有得放，死咗嘅無得返生。"},{"pid":"7d8a36220f07e05a355163ad7ed2a8d978efc5db","tid":1828372,"uid":336575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n之前曾鈺成個講法：輕罪可以特赦<br />\n根本係試水溫<br />\n<br />\n潛移默化等大家覺得好過冇<br />\n接受袋住先"}]}